labels.label: auto_leave_successful
labels.description: Whether the robot fully crossed the ROBOT STARTING LINE during autonomous period
labels.usage_context: Tracked at the end of autonomous period

labels.label: auto_coral_L1_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored in the REEF trough (L1) during autonomous

labels.label: auto_coral_L2_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored on REEF L2 BRANCHES during autonomous

labels.label: auto_coral_L3_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored on REEF L3 BRANCHES during autonomous

labels.label: auto_coral_L4_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored on REEF L4 BRANCHES during autonomous

labels.label: auto_algae_processor_scored
labels.description: Number of ALGAE scored in the PROCESSOR during autonomous

labels.label: auto_starting_position
labels.description: Robot starting location (by driver station or field zone)

labels.label: teleop_coral_L1_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored in the REEF trough (L1) during teleop

labels.label: teleop_coral_L2_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored on REEF L2 BRANCHES during teleop

labels.label: teleop_coral_L3_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored on REEF L3 BRANCHES during teleop

labels.label: teleop_coral_L4_scored
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored on REEF L4 BRANCHES during teleop

labels.label: teleop_algae_processor_scored
labels.description: Number of ALGAE scored in the PROCESSOR during teleop

labels.label: teleop_algae_net_scored
labels.description: Number of ALGAE scored in the NET during teleop

labels.label: teleop_cycles_completed
labels.description: Number of complete game piece cycles (pickup, score, repeat) performed in teleop

labels.label: teleop_pickups_from_coral_station
labels.description: Number of CORAL picked up from the CORAL STATION during teleop

labels.label: teleop_pickups_from_field
labels.description: Number of CORAL or ALGAE picked up from the field (not from station) during teleop

labels.label: endgame_park_achieved
labels.description: Whether the robot parked in the BARGE ZONE at the end of the match

labels.label: endgame_climb_attempted
labels.description: Where Robot Ended at Endgame

labels.label: endgame_climb_successful_shallow
labels.description: Whether the robot successfully climbed onto a shallow CAGE at match end

labels.label: endgame_climb_successful_deep
labels.description: Whether the robot successfully climbed onto a deep CAGE at match end

labels.label: endgame_climb_time
labels.description: Time taken to complete climb onto CAGE in endgame
labels.usage_context: Measured during last 20 seconds of match

labels.label: defense_time_spent
labels.description: Total time spent actively defending against opponents

labels.label: defense_effectiveness_rating
labels.description: Subjective rating of how effective the robot's defense was

labels.label: was_defended_against
labels.description: Whether the robot was actively defended against by opponents

labels.label: defense_penalties_incurred
labels.description: Number of fouls or penalties incurred while playing defense

labels.label: mechanical_failures
labels.description: Number of mechanical failures or breakdowns during the match

labels.label: brownouts_occurred
labels.description: Whether the robot experienced brownouts or power loss during the match

labels.label: overall_reliability_rating
labels.description: Subjective rating of robot's reliability and uptime during the match

labels.label: stuck_or_disabled
labels.description: Whether the robot became stuck or disabled during the match

labels.label: cooperation_with_alliance
labels.description: Subjective rating of how well the robot cooperated with alliance partners

labels.label: field_positioning_effectiveness
labels.description: Subjective rating of robot's field awareness and positioning

labels.label: coopertition_bonus_contributed
labels.description: Whether the robot contributed to achieving the Coopertition Bonus (scoring at least 2 ALGAE in PROCESSOR)

labels.label: barge_rp_contributed
labels.description: Whether the robot contributed to achieving the BARGE RP (scoring at least 16 BARGE points)

labels.label: coral_rp_contributed
labels.description: Whether the robot contributed to achieving the CORAL RP (scoring at least 7 CORAL on each level)

labels.label: auto_net_score
labels.description: The total number of game pieces scored by a robot into the 'Net' scoring area during the autonomous period of a match. This metric reflects the robot's autonomous scoring effectiveness specifically for the Net target.
labels.typical_range: 0-5 (may vary depending on game rules and scoring opportunities)
labels.usage_context: Track this metric during the autonomous period by counting each game piece successfully scored by the robot into the Net. Record immediately after autonomous ends, based on observed scoring or official field data.

labels.label: Teleop Game Piece Score
labels.description: Total number of game pieces scored by the team during the teleoperated period.
labels.usage_context: Tracked live during the match by counting each game piece scored in teleop, recorded after the teleop period ends.

labels.label: strategy_observed
labels.description: Indicates whether a notable team strategy or unique play was observed during the match.
labels.usage_context: Checked if scouts observe a significant strategic action or deviation from standard play during the match.

labels.label: auto_mobility_score
labels.description: Number of times the robot successfully crosses the mobility line during autonomous.
labels.usage_context: Tracked during the autonomous period by observing if the robot fully exits its starting zone for mobility points.

labels.label: Auto Total Points
labels.description: Total number of points scored by the robot during the autonomous period.
labels.usage_context: Recorded after the autonomous period ends, based on the robot's scoring actions as shown on the field display or by manual tally.

labels.label: teleop_total_points
labels.description: Total points scored by the team during the teleoperated period.
labels.usage_context: Tracked live during the teleop phase by summing all point-scoring actions performed by the team.

labels.label: endgame_total_points
labels.description: Total points earned by the team during the endgame period of the match.
labels.usage_context: Recorded at the end of the match by summing all points scored by the team during the endgame phase.

labels.label: strategy_notes
labels.description: General strategic observations and notes about robot performance
labels.usage_context: Recorded throughout match for strategic analysis

labels.label: driver_skill_rating
labels.description: Number of observed driver errors or notable driving maneuvers during the match.
labels.usage_context: Scouted live during each match by counting visible driver mistakes or impressive actions, such as quick recoveries, precise alignment, or evasive maneuvers.

labels.label: strategy_field
labels.description: Briefly describes the primary strategies a team employed on the field during the match.
labels.usage_context: Scouted live during matches to capture notable strategic approaches or shifts observed for each team.

labels.label: scout_comments
labels.description: Free-form notes for recording observations or strategic insights about a team's performance during a match.
labels.usage_context: Entered by scouts during or immediately after a match to capture details not covered by other metrics, such as unique strategies, robot issues, or alliance interactions.

labels.label: Teleop CORAL Scored in Branch (L2-L4)
labels.description: Number of CORAL scored in the Branch (levels 2-4) during the teleoperated period.
labels.usage_context: Tracked live during the teleop period as robots score CORAL in Branch goals at levels 2 through 4.

labels.label: teleop_algae_scored_barge_processor
labels.description: Number of ALGAE scored in the Barge and Processor goals during teleoperated period.
labels.usage_context: Tracked live during the teleop phase as each ALGAE piece is scored in either the Barge or Processor goals.

labels.label: tele_algae_bleed
labels.description: Number of ALGAE game pieces unintentionally sent to the opposing side during teleop.
labels.usage_context: Track each time a team accidentally causes an ALGAE piece to cross into the opposing field during the teleoperated period.
